description: The modern La Nied river, a tributary of the Saar, which runs through parts of modern France and Germany.
details: The Barrington Atlas Directory supplies "Nidda" (a river in the vicinity of Frankfurt) as the modern name, but the map label "Nida" is clearly associated with La Nied.
